query:
UPDATE settings
            SET
                max_concurrent_writes = $1,
                max_concurrent_downloads = $2,

                theme = $3,
                default_page = $4,
                collapsed_navigation = $5,
                advanced_rendering = $6,
                native_decorations = $7,

                discord_rpc = $8,
                developer_mode = $9,
                telemetry = $10,

                onboarded = $11,

                extra_launch_args = jsonb($12),
                custom_env_vars = jsonb($13),
                mc_memory_max = $14,
                mc_force_fullscreen = $15,
                mc_game_resolution_x = $16,
                mc_game_resolution_y = $17,
                hide_on_process_start = $18,

                hook_pre_launch = $19,
                hook_wrapper = $20,
                hook_post_exit = $21,

                custom_dir = $22,
                prev_custom_dir = $23,
                migrated = $24
